org.netbeans.api.maven.archetype

Class Archetype

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.api.maven.archetype.Archetype

  • public final class Archetype
extends Object
    Simple model class to describe a Maven archetype. To be created by ArchetypeProvider implementations, consumed by the New Maven Project wizard.

    1.0
